6. Add required Restaurant JSON-LD schema with availableLanguage set to Spanish and English.
4. Phase 3: Form page rebuild (depends on 2, parallel with Phase 2 after content map is stable)
1. Rebuild application.html with all required fields and correct input types.
2. Ensure each control has associated label (for/id), use fieldset + legend for grouped controls.
3. Add required markers, error containers, and accessible hint/error relationships.
4. Keep mobile-first Tailwind layout with sm/md/lg responsive behavior.
5. Add submit and clear button behavior requirements.
5. Phase 4: Validation and dependent logic (depends on 4)
1. Refactor validation.js into clear sections: constants, validators, dependent-select updates, UI feedback.
2. Implement real-time validation (input/blur/change).
3. Enforce exact required rules and exact error messages from context.
